source.name: Postal Service salaries in Lancaster, Pa.
source.description: Salaries show base pay or hourly rate only and do not include Pay for Performance or other additional payments. Final pay for the year can be substantially lower due to part-time work, or higher due to incentive payments. Source: Asbury Park Press
